The deterministic coverage convention, measured calibration points, and
hot-list file format originate in the pre-existing moe-autopilot research. The
Studio UI, typed analysis engine, protocol-aware evidence model, safe experiment
runner, Codex App Server bridge, offline mode, exports, tests, and distribution
are implemented in this repository. Sanitized fixture manifests retain hashes
of their local source artifacts.

No DeltaMoE clinical hardsets or domain-training data are distributed here.
